msgid "Are you sure you'll be okay?"
msgstr "你確定會沒事嗎？"

msgid "Yeah for sure!"
msgstr "當然了！"

msgid "Tip top shape."
msgstr "狀況好得很。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "Take your time."
msgstr "慢慢來。"

msgid "I mean... it's not like I'm bleeding out or anything."
msgstr "反正...我又沒有在流血。"

msgid "(I need to find an exit fast.)"
msgstr "(我需要快點找到出口。)"

msgid "Sai is not moving."
msgstr "賽伊不動了。"

msgid "She's back..... She's back."
msgstr "她回來了...她回來了。"

msgid "She's singing in my ears....."
msgstr "她在我的耳邊歌唱..."

msgid "Singing all the time....."
msgstr "一直在歌唱..."

msgid "Humming..."
msgstr "哼著歌..."

msgid "Burning..."
msgstr "燃燒著..."

msgid "Oh no... burning...."
msgstr "喔不...燃燒著..."

msgid "Hahahahaha....."
msgstr "哈哈哈哈哈....."

msgid "Burning."
msgstr "燃燒著。"
